{"tid":1968820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩歲細佬成日睇唔知咩野...","createTime":"2020-04-12T03:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T08:23:33.000Z","uid":313064,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"78c216b553ecf7c467ed445de2edd83589e667ae","tid":1968820,"uid":313064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"咁宜家都係電子奶咀既年代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬日日都要睇幾個鐘youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初初睇都係兒歌個啲（baby shark個啲好大路既野）<br />\n但最近佢成日睇啲兒歌係變速阿倒帶、較低音高音、負片個啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越睇越不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一轉走佢就發哂脾氣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知做咩會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da57321cbfcc314a6c5d36d7cebde177042970fd","tid":1968820,"uid":313064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e491e70cb4265d97e11cf670862ed3376a3b461","tid":1968820,"uid":301989,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"兩歲就用電子野真係害咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941b3edc40666edc4f235b59d328332428aa1a7d","tid":1968820,"uid":235579,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78c216b553ecf7c467ed445de2edd83589e667ae","tid":1968820,"uid":313064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"咁宜家都係電子奶咀既年代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬日日都要睇幾個鐘youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初初睇都係兒歌個啲（baby shark個啲好大路既野）<br />\n但最近佢成日睇啲兒歌係變速阿倒帶、較低音高音、負片個啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越睇越不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一轉走佢就發哂脾氣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知做咩會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"小朋友係唔應該店電子產品，會上癮。<br />\n<br />\n轉走發嬲係正常，因為係毒品。<br />\n<br />\n你點都要忍下佢鬧，拎走部機。"},{"pid":"c0c72b98f8ff67b3d70c6e792d70727b219de8a9","tid":1968820,"uid":91471,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"Elsagate<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c323a92cec891b449d836ac86d11065dbd9968a","tid":1968820,"uid":332538,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78c216b553ecf7c467ed445de2edd83589e667ae","tid":1968820,"uid":313064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"咁宜家都係電子奶咀既年代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬日日都要睇幾個鐘youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初初睇都係兒歌個啲（baby shark個啲好大路既野）<br />\n但最近佢成日睇啲兒歌係變速阿倒帶、較低音高音、負片個啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越睇越不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一轉走佢就發哂脾氣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲知做咩會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"至少升小學先俾佢惦，調教時間，每日一個鐘，但可累積，例如星期一至六無玩，星期日可以俾佢玩合共七個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n中學加到兩個鐘至三個鐘不等。<br />\n<br />\n基本上是毒品來，防礙智力發展，但完全唔俾佢用又唔得，要拎個平衡。"},{"pid":"26502cbbfd8b2b629f502ed6256a046c839ca243","tid":1968820,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"parental lock 都唔識用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd864de49e9fed9811789b5cc724d0652bf86f8","tid":1968820,"uid":46345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26502cbbfd8b2b629f502ed6256a046c839ca243","tid":1968820,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"parental lock 都唔識用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"用咗parental lock都會睇到<br />\n例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gF4l--oNW2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgF4l--oNW2Q&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fff8d531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gF4l--oNW2Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P8_5p_tqsmA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP8_5p_tqsmA&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=5827c334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P8_5p_tqsmA</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人知道點解啲細路會鐘意睇呢啲片？ 我都見過小朋友睇，睇到入咗神，坐定定睇啲重覆又重覆好洗腦嘅片"},{"pid":"0c48b501458a60a7f5fa35cb3332e3e6b582e556","tid":1968820,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"唔比轉走就打佢一巴"},{"pid":"8c244b717cf9bb5620d32b94c52487ac0bdec994","tid":1968820,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:04:08.000Z","msg":"唔好畀佢玩呢啲，試下陪下佢？"},{"pid":"9b2258a9e591731952baa