49ca163bdb0530f8fb112","tid":1968820,"uid":56541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"小心autoplay會播到啲有問題嘅片<br />\n<br />\n愛莎門（英語：Elsagate）是一個新詞，指的是在YouTube和YouTube Kids（英語：YouTube Kids）上上載的所謂對兒童友好的影片的爭議，大部分此類影片包含的主題並不適合兒童，比如呈現暴力、性愛、戀物癖和廁所幽默等內容，以及涉及危險或破壞的情況和活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E8%8E%8E%E9%97%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2589%25BE%25E8%258E%258E%25E9%2597%25A8&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=ebabd45b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E8%8E%8E%E9%97%A8</a>"},{"pid":"22d11bf668c0be97f489e6a0434de505716bfc25","tid":1968820,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c65602e00d5d83116149ca163bdb0530f8fb112","tid":1968820,"uid":56541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"小心autoplay會播到啲有問題嘅片<br />\n<br />\n愛莎門（英語：Elsagate）是一個新詞，指的是在YouTube和YouTube Kids（英語：YouTube Kids）上上載的所謂對兒童友好的影片的爭議，大部分此類影片包含的主題並不適合兒童，比如呈現暴力、性愛、戀物癖和廁所幽默等內容，以及涉及危險或破壞的情況和活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E8%8E%8E%E9%97%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2589%25BE%25E8%258E%258E%25E9%2597%25A8&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=ebabd45b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E8%8E%8E%E9%97%A8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/2d/Thumbnails_of_Elsagate_content.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F2d%2FThumbnails_of_Elsagate_content.jpg&h=0f88fabb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b05a08b3a42267436dd075344141ecc2098711a3","tid":1968820,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"兩歲睇YouTube 係害咗佢。<br />\n你咪逃避問題"},{"pid":"87df8d5fddca959c4e9f66a5a2116a3608d69514","tid":1968820,"uid":9115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4fd864de49e9fed9811789b5cc724d0652bf86f8","tid":1968820,"uid":46345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26502cbbfd8b2b629f502ed6256a046c839ca243","tid":1968820,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"parental lock 都唔識用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"用咗parental lock都會睇到<br />\n例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gF4l--oNW2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgF4l--oNW2Q&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fff8d531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gF4l--oNW2Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P8_5p_tqsmA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP8_5p_tqsmA&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=5827c334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P8_5p_tqsmA</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人知道點解啲細路會鐘意睇呢啲片？ 我都見過小朋友睇，睇到入咗神，坐定定睇啲重覆又重覆好洗腦嘅片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"其實,係我地要掉返轉諗<br />\n點解我地睇呢d片會覺得不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實好大部分係來自電視,電影之類<br />\n<br />\n例如,我地見綠色會覺得係恐怖<br />\n點解呢？因為以前d恐怖片習慣用綠色去表達嘛<br />\n好似阿凡達咁,皮膚變藍色,唔通件事唔恐怖咩？<br />\n但係我地第一個主觀感覺只會覺得「奇怪」,但唔會係「恐怖」<br />\n所以呢個其實係我地受電視,電影嘅影響<br />\n對顏色有先入為主<br />\n<br />\nd細路反而無我地咁多呢d先入為主<br />\n呢d片對佢嚟講都係新事物,咁咪鍾意睇囉<br />\n我個人覺得,呢d純graphic變化嘅片,睇下又無妨嘅"},{"pid":"306cbf4a7c6e5c888838b622ecc41598ece5b3b0","tid":1968820,"uid":256094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"記得之前有人分析過暗網有啲變態嘅兒童心理學家專門做呢一類嘅片放上YouTube<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係一啲扭曲左嘅音樂圖畫以及強烈嘅顏色刺激之下放入一啲悉心安排過嘅訊息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲片記得都有啲共通點就係成年人睇落會覺得有種講唔出嘅怪同不適<br />\n<br />\n更加何況有Elsa gate 同Momo之類變態內容<br 